5_30	0.09901141	, which received a significantly lower price, Microsoft says, because it shared in the costs of developing Windows 95 _ a straightforward business rationale for different terms, says Microsoft, not punishment meted out by a monopolist.
5_31	0.12898079	But the government introduced an IBM document that cast doubt on Microsoft's statement.
